=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交通：<br />\n冇得同市區/鐵路沿線比，但當佢村屋地段，預左要揸車。去荃灣青衣尚可<br />\n<br />\n飲食：<br />\n來來去去都係果十間八間，唔悶怕其實冇問題，收工食埋先返屋企又得。三間超市一個街市+HKTVMALL = 自煮尚可<br />\n<br />\n環境：<br />\n較潮濕，晚上有賽車嘈音，但大致清幽<br />\n<br />\n投資價值：<br />\n不要再說了.jpg<br />\n<br />\n優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n環境：<br />\n青山綠水冇的彈，有小朋友去行山沙灘都方便；尺價較低，細極都四五百尺起，適合人類居住<br />\n<br />\n人口結構：<br />\n區內冇政府房屋，以私樓村屋為主，多年輕家庭，居民質素較佳。<br />\n<br />\n租/買成本：<br />\n低<br />\n<br />\n當年考慮咗好耐先搬入&amp;搬走<br />\nIf too long, Sorry1999"},{"pid":"629f54c6ed26d069b724c6fafd305b8df5051724","tid":1137310,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T01:59:25.000Z","msg":"我坐青山灣既<br />\n坐962行下路過曬深井往屯門方向，對面線會有D house<br />\n我有次一望入去，哇個樓底高到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚羨幕"},{"pid":"90168c2b9f2f26e4546ded2378a93e0e50e7831c","tid":1137310,"uid":11097,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ed3cf5d18e9262a24322ea4554e328cf19b0016e","tid":1137310,"uid":52323,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"成個私樓地段不知幾正，景又靚又靜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T02:01:45.000Z","msg":"最重要最重要<br />\n冇支那豚"},{"pid":"6e9426239e92f383d3e278ed80802c843e2015da","tid":1137310,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T02:23:19.000Z","msg":"好撚唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />住左半年即搬走"},{"pid":"21c20fb3a670c8b49a87efa10e6ca95f41881ccd","tid":1137310,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e50c983bbf77dedc63e1a0d7bab2bc028a47d677","tid":1137310,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"一出屯門公路就好似入左個小社區咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T02:28:04.000Z","msg":"青山公路呀"},{"pid":"07b3529f243071d5c7301b4ad76ac248209d6653","tid":1137310,"uid":103981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"c